      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="7401st">7401st meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2015-03-06" refersTo="#adoptionDate">6 March 2015</docDate></docTitle>
